{"tid":237244,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"內地男石澳游水 體力不支嗌救命","createTime":"2017-05-10T09:00:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-10T09:27:06.000Z","uid":122,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2782ad4cc37f51fafd47ad9949b5b0f966fc676e","tid":237244,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T09:00:55.000Z","msg":"內地男石澳游水 體力不支嗌救命<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170510/large/1494406317_6014.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170510%2Flarge%2F1494406317_6014.jpg&h=86a8ad0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n石澳下午發生泳客遇溺事件！一名26歲內地男子偕朋友到石澳泳灘游水，至下午2時許，事主懷疑體力不支，揮手求救，友人立即上前拖住，在場的救生員發現後將他救起。事主獲救時神志清醒，由救護車送院治理。"},{"pid":"141545afa18c0b42e2ea6967bc95c1088512a89c","tid":237244,"uid":3974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T09:22:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">渣ga</span></span>"},{"pid":"8a4003e8e006452a5e81181506efa736d4238bcf","tid":237244,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T09:27:06.000Z","msg":"水鬼本身想話搵替死鬼<br />\n<br />\n聽到佢用大陸豬口音叫救命就即刻收手"}]}